<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟和简跑出了多特服装店，一直跑到游戏商店才停下脚步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“警察来了吗？”简喘着气问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟四处看看：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得没有，但我们应该找到男孩子们，然后离开这里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41373</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们并没有找很长时间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在那时，赛伊和鲍比从游戏商店门里冲了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在他们身后，店员正挥舞着拳头威胁着他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>相互交换了一个无助的眼神之后，孩子们开始沿着街道奔跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得休息一会了。”几分钟后潘瑟大叫道，“我们能不能停下来？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊领着孩子们去了一个公园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81547</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们瘫倒在了几张长椅上，坐在那里大口喘着气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你买了你的游戏了吗？”潘瑟问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的声音现在平静一点了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊向他的妹妹们解释了刚才发生的情况。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比一句话没说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他依然在生赛伊的气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>之后潘瑟也告诉了她的兄弟们多特服装店里发生的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可能变得有钱了，但这些金币对我们来说一点儿好处都没有。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊总结道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个人都对他的看法表示赞同。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“而且我很过分，简。”潘瑟说，“对不起。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也很抱歉，潘瑟。”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144878</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，你穿那条裙子很好看。”简拥抱了她的姐姐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144879</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿，卖冰淇淋的人来了！”赛伊大叫着跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑向了一边播放音乐，一边朝这边开来的一辆冰淇淋车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的姐妹们和他一起去了，但鲍比跟在后面，拖拖拉拉地走着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我请客。”赛伊主动说，“你们想吃哪种都可以。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟和简都选了草莓口味加巧克力酱，赛伊则选择香草焦糖口味。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿，鲍比！”赛伊大声叫着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么不来个巧克力棉花糖味道的呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我什么都不想要。不要再对我指手画脚了！”鲍比嚷了回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他孩子都你看看我，我看看你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216315</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他还在生我的气。”赛伊耸耸肩，“他会很快忘了这件事情的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊将他留在口袋里的两枚金币递给了卖冰淇淋的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人摇摇头说：“这是什么？游戏币？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊对着那个人懒懒地笑了一下，拿出了他的钱包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用自己的钱付了冰淇淋的钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们朝家走去的时候， 太阳刚开始往下落。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>变得富有的愿望很快就要结束了，一切都会回到从前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，鲍比是第一个醒来的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他悄悄地穿好了衣服，并在太阳一升起的时候就溜出了房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天轮到鲍比许愿了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很清楚自己想要什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他穿过森林，找到了那口古井。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“休伊，休伊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294224</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比一边焦急地叫着，一边将木桶从井底拉了上来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294225</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊慢慢从他的壳里探出头来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他满脸睡意地看着鲍比：“你知道现在是什么时间吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要许愿。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他完全无视了休伊的表情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“其他人在哪里？”休伊四处看了看问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没关系的。今天轮到我许愿了。”鲍比迅速回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊饶有兴趣地盯着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，那么，你的愿望是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>340513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比闭上了眼睛说：“我希望我是家里唯一的孩子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>